AirBuddFormBuilder
==================

A form builder that generates semantic HTML as advocated by Andy Budd in CSS Mastery.


Example
=======

app/views/projects/new.html.erb:

  <% airbudd_form_for @project do |f| %>
    <%= f.text_field :title %>
  <% end %>


